Newtonia is a top down 2D space shooter.
Written in C++ using GLUT and OpenGL.

Global Keys:
 fullscreen: f
      pause: p
       quit: esc 

(two players works best with 2 USB keyboards)

Player 1 Keys:
  thrust: w
 reverse: s
    left: a
   right: f
   shoot: space
    mine: x

Player 2 Keys:
  thrust: i
 reverse: k
    left: j
   right: l
   shoot: /
    mine: ,
